            },
            {
              "answer": "Start with occupancy rate, average daily rate, total revenue, length of stay, and cancellation rate. MyAllocator tracks them all automatically.",
              "question": "Which KPIs Should Hosts Monitor?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Divide booked nights by available nights, then multiply by 100. Example: 287 booked nights ÷ 365 available nights × 100 = 78.6 % occupancy.",
              "question": "How Do I Calculate Occupancy Rate?"
            },
